STEP 5: CLOSING (What would you improve?)
-----------------------------------------------

"If I were to improve this project:

First, migrate from class components to functional components with 
React Hooks — useContext, useState, useEffect. This would reduce 
boilerplate and make the code more readable.

Second, persist saved videos in localStorage so they survive page 
refreshes — right now they're lost because they're only in memory.

Third, add infinite scrolling or pagination for the home page 
instead of loading all videos at once.

Fourth, implement the search functionality with debouncing — so 
the API isn't called on every keystroke but waits until the user 
stops typing."


